#    -*- mode: org -*-

* Introduction

This directory contains source code for various eyes-free
applications for the Android platform.
It will also contain supporting code and libraries such as TTS.

* Build Instructions

Each of these eyes-free applications can be built with a simple
command-line of the form:

:ant -Dsdk-folder=<android-sdk-root>

Thus, to build the Talking Dialer, 
: cd talkingdialer
: ant-Dsdk-folder=<android-sdk-root>


* List Of Eyes-Free Applications

Each application is found in its own sub-directory.

| Name           | Description                       | Directory     |
|----------------+-----------------------------------+---------------|
| Compass        | Talking Compass                   | compass       |
| Mem            | The Android Memory Game           | androidsays   |
| TalkingDialer  | Talking Dialer Using Stroke Input | talkingdialer |
| Shell          | Eyes-Free Shell                   | shell         |
| Common Library | Jars used by all applications     | commonlib     |
| Third Party    | Third Party Code                  | thirdparty    |
|----------------+-----------------------------------+---------------|

